what is css?
make used for HTML designing in proper manner

full form -> cascading style sheet

syntax -> 
selector { property : value ; }

css - basic 
css3 - advanced

how many was to create css?
inline -> used with style attribute in particular element
internal -> apply in <style> tag 
external -> create a new file with filename.css extension

what are selectors ?
1) element selector 
for ex, p { height : 200px} where p is a paragraph tag

2) class selector 
for ex, .myclass { height : 200px }

3) ID selector 
for ex, #myid { height : 200px }

4) univarsal selector 
for ex, * { height : 200px }

5) group selector
for ex, h1,h2,h3 { color : red ;}